author: ian_dickinson
msg: Fixed bug in OntModel.listInstances, which was using the query engine
machinery, and thereby forking a thread, when not necessary for direct
cases of listInstances. Also changed DIGREasonerFactory to show that
it supports direct version of instance listing.

author: chris-dollin
msg: Models now have a read( URL, baseURI, language ) method.

author: ian_dickinson
msg: Added a fix to prevent leakage of rule_variable marker out to other
subsystems, in particular which was causing a failure in the rdb model
